How to change node version throgh cli 

//without downloading from website change it.

just check nvm is there or not in cli ?
to check type     nvm --version 
if not there install nvm by -- 

curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.1/install.sh| bash

close the terminal and reopen and check the version nvm --version it should show the version 

now install node throght cli 
nvm i {nodeVersiontype}
